Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.85,0:00:36.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑\N{\fs38}Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.69,0:00:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 动手\N{\fs38}Morty, do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.52,0:00:41.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快摁按钮\N{\fs38}Hit the button now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.55,0:00:42.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做不到 Rick\N{\fs38}I can't do it, Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.31,0:00:43.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是我的爸妈和姐姐啊\N{\fs38}They're my parents and sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.82,0:00:45.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 我已经和你说过了 这不是你家人\N{\fs38}Morty, I already told you it's not your family!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.50,0:00:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是另一个未来的平行宇宙里\N{\fs38}They're clones from an alternate reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.10,0:00:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被外星恶灵附身的他们\N{\fs38}possessed by demonic alien spirits from another dimension's future!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.25,0:00:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是得要什么记忆辅助装置之类的吗\N{\fs38}Do you need a mnemonic device or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.80,0:00:53.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快摁按钮\N{\fs38}Just hit the button, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.09,0:00:57.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 Morty 我爱你 亲爱的\N{\fs38}Morty, please, I love you, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.02,0:00:58.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢\N{\fs38}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.81,0:01:06.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好 Morty\N{\fs38}Good work, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.52,0:01:11.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这这这些外星恶灵可是非常珍贵的\N{\fs38}You know, th-th-these demonic alien spirits are really valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.55,0:01:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吗 Morty\N{\fs38}You okay, Morty?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.52,0:01:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你说了那些金枪鱼不能吃了\N{\fs38}I told you not to trust that tuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.19,0:01:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不管他们究竟是什么\N{\fs38}I just killed my family!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.65,0:01:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚杀了我的家人\N{\fs38}I don't care what they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.02,0:01:17.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 Morty\N{\fs38}I don't know, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.68,0:01:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的人出大价钱就为了迈出这一步呢\N{\fs38}Some people'd pay top dollar for that kind of breakthrough.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.62,0:01:21.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rick 我受够了\N{\fs38}You know what, Rick? That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.22,0:01:23.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受够这些疯狂的冒险了\N{\fs38}I'm done with these insane adventures!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.80,0:01:25.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心灵受到了创伤\N{\fs38}That was really traumatizing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.19,0:01:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不干了\N{\fs38}I quit! I'm out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.15,0:01:27.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 哇 哇\N{\fs38}Whoa, whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.19,0:01:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别啊 Morty 别别别这样\N{\fs38}Come on, Morty, don't don't don't be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.32,0:01:30.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙就是这样疯狂而混乱的啊\N{\fs38}The universe is a crazy, chaotic place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.79,0:01:32.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才疯狂又混乱\N{\fs38}You're the one that's crazy and chaotic!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.29,0:01:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冒险应该是轻松愉快才对\N{\fs38}Adventures are supposed to be simple and fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.80,0:01:36.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 Morty 是啊\N{\fs38}Oh, yeah, Morty, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.11,0:01:38.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这这这这种话 跟班的说起来当然轻松\N{\fs38}Yeah, that that that's real easy to say from the sidekick position.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.46,0:01:40.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那那不然下次 你来负责\N{\fs38}But but, uh, how about next time you be in charge,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.82,0:01:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们看看是怎么个轻松愉快法\N{\fs38}and then we'll talk about how simple and fun it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.82,0:01:43.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗 Rick\N{\fs38}Seriously, Rick?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.82,0:01:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你让我来做决定吗\N{\fs38}Y-y-you'll you'll let me call the shots?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:46.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs38}Okay, yeah, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.89,0:01:49.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过为了更有意思些 Morty\N{\fs38}But let's make it interesting, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.42,0:01:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如如如果你的冒险很烂 我们半路放弃了\N{\fs38}I-I-I-if your adventure sucks and we bail halfway through it,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.41,0:01:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那以后的冒险你都不准抱怨\N{\fs38}you lose the right to bitch about all future adventures.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.32,0:01:56.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 你得帮我洗一个月的衣服\N{\fs38}Plus, you have to do my laundry for a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.29,0:01:57.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题 硬汉\N{\fs38}Okay, all right, tough guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.75,0:01:59.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果成功的话\N{\fs38}But if my adventure's good,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.01,0:02:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后每三个冒险就由我做主\N{\fs38}I get to be in charge of every third adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.92,0:02:01.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每十个\N{\fs38}Every tenth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.61,0:02:02.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成交\N{\fs38}Deal. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.42,0:02:03.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那那我们快点出发吧\N{\fs38}W-well, come on, let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.90,0:02:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸 洗碗机老毛病又犯了\N{\fs38}Dad, the dishwasher's doing that thing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.90,0:02:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗碗的毛病么\N{\fs38}Washing dishes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.80,0:02:09.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 它不洗啊 你能修好它么  - Rick外公\N{\fs38}- No. The opposite. Can you fix it? - Grandpa Rick,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.30,0:02:10.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我作业不会做 能帮帮我吗\N{\fs38}Can you help me with my science homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.84,0:02:12.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以啊 别做就好啦\N{\fs38}Yeah j-just don't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.30,0:02:12.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外公\N{\fs38}Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.61,0:02:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rick 你有什么手状的发明\N{\fs38}Hey, Rick, you got some kind of hand-shaped device
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.46,0:02:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能帮我打开这美乃滋的罐子嘛\N{\fs38}that can open this mayonnaise jar?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.92,0:02:18.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 帽子戏法(三连击)\N{\fs38}Wow. Hat trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 Morty 冒险的事情先暂且放一下吧\N{\fs38}All right, Morty, let's put a pin in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.31,0:02:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你家这群可怜虫需要我的帮助\N{\fs38}I got to help your pathetic family.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:22.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说这种话 你不是怂(鸡)了吧\N{\fs38}Oh, that sounds like something a chicken would say.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.85,0:02:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咯咯咯 咯咯咯\N{\fs38}Bawk, bawk, bawk, bawk, bawk, bawk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.41,0:02:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵 Morty 你真是欺人太甚了 赌约正式开始\N{\fs38}Oh, Morty, you done did it this time. It's on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.01,0:02:29.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是等不及你的冒险不终而散\N{\fs38}I can't wait to watch your adventure lay a huge fart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.53,0:02:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至于你们这群渣渣\N{\fs38}As for you dingdongs...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.60,0:02:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是一个使命必达盒\N{\fs38}This is a Meeseeks Box.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:35.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来示范一下 你按这个\N{\fs38}Let me show you how it works. You press this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:38.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看过来 我是使命必达先生\N{\fs38}I'm Mr. Meeseeks! Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:39.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说出你的请求\N{\fs38}You make a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.17,0:02:41.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使命必达先生 打开Jerry的傻逼美乃滋罐子\N{\fs38}Mr. Meeseeks, open Jerry's stupid mayonnaise jar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.79,0:02:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命 先生\N{\fs38}Yes, siree!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.98,0:02:44.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使命必达先生会满足你的请求\N{\fs38}The Meeseeks fulfills the request.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.00,0:02:46.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞定\N{\fs38}All done!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.04,0:02:46.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇\N{\fs38}Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.75,0:02:48.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后他会自动消失\N{\fs38}And then it stops existing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.54,0:02:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪 他自爆了\N{\fs38}Oh, my god, he exploded!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.12,0:02:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 他们巴不得这样\N{\fs38}Trust me, they're fine with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:54.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请便 但记得请求不要太复杂\N{\fs38}Knock yourselves out, just keep your requests simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.75,0:02:56.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们可不是上帝\N{\fs38}They're not gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.09,0:02:58.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行 好了 快点出去吧 大家快滚出去\N{\fs38}All right! G-get out of here now! Everybody out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.16,0:02:59.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有场赌要赢呢\N{\fs38}I got a bet to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.60,0:03:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好多心愿想实现啊\N{\fs38}So many possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.10,0:03:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脑中一片翻腾\N{\fs38}My mind is racing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:04.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们要用这东西的话\N{\fs38}If we're gonna use this thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.63,0:03:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我觉得还是有点玄 我们的请求得简...\N{\fs38}which I'm not even sure we should, we need to keep it simp...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.90,0:03:08.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是使命必达先生\N{\fs38}I'm Mr. Meeseeks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.34,0:03:09.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想在学校里变得受欢迎\N{\fs38}I want to be popular at school!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.39,0:03:10.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行啊\N{\fs38}Ooh, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.78,0:03:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Summer 我刚刚还在说来着\N{\fs38}Summer, what did I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.15,0:03:14.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是使命必达先生 看过来\N{\fs38}Ooh, I'm Mr. Meeseeks! Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.53,0:03:16.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想成为一个更加完整的女人\N{\fs38}I-I-I want I want to be a more complete woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:16.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs38}Beth\NBeth!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 行啊 女士\N{\fs38}Oh, yeah! Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.03,0:03:21.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这是在乱用吧\N{\fs38}You guys are doing it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.40,0:03:23.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说了要"简单"\N{\fs38}He said "simple."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.99,0:03:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 我是使命必达先生\N{\fs38}Hey, there. I'm Mr. Meeseeks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.99,0:03:31.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使命必达先生 我希望我的高尔夫成绩能减两杆\N{\fs38}Mr. Meeseeks, I would like to take two strokes off my golf game.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.95,0:03:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行啊 没问题\N{\fs38}Ooh, yeah! Can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.80,0:03:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞定\N{\fs38}Nailed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.24,0:03:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪 Morty 这冒险开始得好无聊啊\N{\fs38}God, Morty, what a boring start to an adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.30,0:03:41.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们干嘛不直接去肯塔基州啊\N{\fs38}I don't w-w-w-why didn't we just go to Kentucky?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.66,0:03:45.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rick 这是一个奇幻世界 里面充满了神奇的生物和奇幻的东西\N{\fs38}Rick, this is a fantasy-type world with creatures and all sorts of fantasy things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.68,0:03:48.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我们是来探险的  - 好期待啊\N{\fs38}- W-we're going on a quest, okay? - Can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咳咳 不好意思\N{\fs38}Ahem. Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是两位渴望冒险的谦逊英雄\N{\fs38}We are two humble heroes in search of adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.19,0:03:56.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪 太丢脸了\N{\fs38}Oh, my god, so embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.39,0:03:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们总算来了 两位英雄 你们得帮帮我们\N{\fs38}At last! Two heroes! You must help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.16,0:04:01.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个村太穷了\N{\fs38}This village is terribly poor,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.19,0:04:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是住在云端的巨人\N{\fs38}yet the giant that lives in the clouds above
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.58,0:04:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却私藏了数不清的财富\N{\fs38}has untold treasures!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.65,0:04:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊\N{\fs38}You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接受你的请求 这位善良又温和的先生\N{\fs38}I-I-I accept your call to adventure, good sir, kind sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.01,0:04:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 Rick 云端上住着巨人呢\N{\fs38}Come on, Rick. There's a giant in the clouds!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.75,0:04:14.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵 新手的运气\N{\fs38}Yeah. Beginner's luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.24,0:04:19.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总而言之 与Summer Smith的友谊是可贵的\N{\fs38}In conclusion, a friendship with Summer Smith is the most valuable
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.70,0:04:18.16,11,,0,0,0,,{\frx352\fry16\frz355.5\pos(576,152.001)}{\fs36}{\fs50}和Summer友谊天长地久
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.74,0:04:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能让你们年轻的生命更加充实\N{\fs38}and enriching experience of your young lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:25.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是使命必达先生 看过来\N{\fs38}I'm Mr. Meeseeks! Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.80,0:04:26.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs38}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使命必达先生是吗\N{\fs38}Uh, Mr. Meeseeks, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:29.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是基恩 阴道\N{\fs38}Yeah. Gene Vagina.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.42,0:04:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最近因为监护权和前妻有点问题 我想能不能\N{\fs38}Listen, I'm in a bit of custody thing with my ex and was wondering...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:34.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 我找Summer要你的联系方式好了\N{\fs38}No, I'll g-get your info from Summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:36.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我17岁时就怀孕了\N{\fs38}I got pregnant at 17.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.95,0:04:38.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是上完了兽医学院\N{\fs38}I mean, I still put myself through veterinary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.77,0:04:43.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很成功 但要是当时我没能\N{\fs38}Yes, I'm successful, but what if I hadn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.44,0:04:47.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想说 时过境迁\N{\fs38}I'm just saying, somewhere along the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.56,0:04:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个天真烂漫的马斯基根少女已经不复存在了\N{\fs38}I lost that wide-eyed girl from Muskegon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.23,0:04:53.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还在你心里啊 Beth\N{\fs38}She's still there, Beth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.42,0:04:55.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少腰是没了\N{\fs38}Well, her waistline isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.53,0:04:59.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Beth 即使有了家庭\N{\fs38}Beth, having a family
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:05:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也还是可以拥有属于自己的一片天啊\N{\fs38}doesn't mean that you stop being an individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:05.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对爱你 依赖你的人\N{\fs38}You know the best thing you can do for people that depend on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:09.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你更应该坦诚 即使这意味着放手\N{\fs38}Be honest with them, even if it means setting them free.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:12.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的意思是说 我应该离开Jerry\N{\fs38}You're saying I should leave Jerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:16.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不敢相信 终于有人谈到了我的心声\N{\fs38}I can't believe I'm finally having this conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.40,0:05:26.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要酒吗\N{\fs38}More wine?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.68,0:05:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用 我喝得够多了\N{\fs38}I think I've had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.80,0:05:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肩放松 自然往后收 Jerry\N{\fs38}Remember to square your shoulders, Jerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.38,0:05:37.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 是啊 我知道了\N{\fs38}Yeah, yeah. I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.72,0:05:45.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的啦 看过来 我是使命必达先生\N{\fs38}That's okay. I'm Mr. Meeseeks! Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:47.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一次 头压低一点\N{\fs38}Try again and keep your head down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以到底要干嘛\N{\fs38}Okay, well, which is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.52,0:05:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收肩还是头压低一点\N{\fs38}Square my shoulders or keep my head down?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:54.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个都要 但是最重要的是 你得放轻松\N{\fs38}Well, it's both. But most importantly, you got to relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.38,0:05:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使命必达先生\N{\fs38}You know what, Mr. Meeseeks?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这样没用 我放弃了\N{\fs38}I don't think this is working. I give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:06:00.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 Jerry 你不能放弃\N{\fs38}I'm sorry, Jerry, but it doesn't work like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.08,0:06:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是使命必达先生\N{\fs38}I'm Mr. Meeseeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:05.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须满足你的请求然后消失 看过来\N{\fs38}I have to fulfill my purpose so I can go away. Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.31,0:06:07.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你随意吧 我逊爆了\N{\fs38}Well, make yourself comfortable, because I suck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.81,0:06:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我才逊爆了\N{\fs38}No, Jerry, I'm the one who sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.37,0:06:11.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我试试这个办法\N{\fs38}Let me try something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.08,0:06:14.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是使命必达先生 看过来\N{\fs38}I'm Mr. Meeseeks! Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.63,0:06:17.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 嗨 使命必达先生 我是使命必达先生 看过来  - 嗨\N{\fs38}- Hi, Mr. Meeseeks! I'm Mr. Meeseeks! Look at me. - Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能帮我让Jerry的高尔夫成绩少两杆嘛\N{\fs38}Can you help me get two strokes off of Jerry's golf swing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.67,0:06:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然可以 我是使命必达先生\N{\fs38}Can do! I'm Mr. Meeseeks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的肩有往后收嘛\N{\fs38}Is he keeping his shoulders squared?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.25,0:06:27.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他有在努力\N{\fs38}Ooh, he's trying!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:33.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 Mort\N{\fs38}All right, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.49,0:06:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们到了这蠢巨人的城堡里面了\N{\fs38}W-w-we're in your stupid giant's castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:37.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来做什么\N{\fs38}W-what do we do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.15,0:06:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放轻松行吗 Rick\N{\fs38}Would you just relax, Rick?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.34,0:06:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只要找到宝藏室就行了\N{\fs38}All we got to do is find the treasure room, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:41.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简单明了\N{\fs38}It's nice and simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.22,0:06:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冒险这么这么一帆风顺真是对不起啊\N{\fs38}You know, I-I-I'm sorry everything's going so smoothly and adventurously.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,0:06:48.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了 Morty\N{\fs38}Uh-oh, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.02,0:06:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情不太妙了啊\N{\fs38}Startin' to get a little hairy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.36,0:06:50.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老大 我们接下来该怎么做\N{\fs38}What do you want to do, boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.42,0:06:52.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点 躲到这个饼干罐后面\N{\fs38}Come on, hurry. Behind this cookie jar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.28,0:06:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(杰克与豌豆中巨人所念四行诗的第一句)\N{\fs38}Fee! Fi! Fo! Fum!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.07,0:06:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放弃吧 Morty 游戏到此为止\N{\fs38}Just give up, Morty. This is game over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:07:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你开口 我们现在就能回去\N{\fs38}I'll take us home right now. You just say the word.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.02,0:07:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没戏 Rick 这都是冒险的一部分\N{\fs38}No way, Rick. This is all part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.06,0:07:05.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冒险就是要有冲突 要勇敢直面\N{\fs38}Adventures have conflict. Deal with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.47,0:07:07.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我闻到了...(第二句 我闻到了英国人的血味)\N{\fs38}I smell the blood of...(an English man)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.87,0:07:10.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我操  - 天哪\N{\fs38}- Holy crap. - Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:11.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他看起来快不行了 Morty\N{\fs38}He looks pretty bad down there, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.87,0:07:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要失血而亡了\N{\fs38}Looks like he's bleeding out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.37,0:07:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪 Dale\N{\fs38}Oh, Jesus! Dale!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.63,0:07:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你们这群混蛋  - 不好\N{\fs38}- You sons of bitches! - Oh, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.73,0:07:20.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,911吗\N{\fs38}Hello, 911?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.97,0:07:22.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我老公被迷你人袭击了\N{\fs38}My husband has been attacked by tiny people!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.81,0:07:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经奄奄一息了\N{\fs38}He's dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:27.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 我们懂\N{\fs38}Hey, look, we get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:29.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们很小 最近又不太景气 然后你们就想\N{\fs38}You're little, you're down on your luck, you think,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"反正他是个巨人\N{\fs38}"Hey, he's a giant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.45,0:07:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妨我们潜入他家 先抢劫再杀人灭口 多好啊"\N{\fs38}Why don't we break into his home, rob him, and murder him?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.77,0:07:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情的经过不是这样子的\N{\fs38}But that's not how it went down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.75,0:07:36.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没差 反正事情就这么入案了\N{\fs38}Oh, well, it's going down like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个就这么入狱吧\N{\fs38}You're both going down like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 Morty 你真是让我见识到了怎么冒险啊\N{\fs38}Ooh, boy, Morty, you're really showing me how it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.49,0:07:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是简单又有趣\N{\fs38}Real straightforward and fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放下想要变得受欢迎这个想法\N{\fs38}Like, letting go of the need to be popular
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:47.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才能更好地让别人喜欢你\N{\fs38}is what makes people like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:50.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真爱来自自爱\N{\fs38}The most important love you can receive is from yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jerry 虎口下握 靠近击球点\N{\fs38}Okay, Jerry, you got to just choke up on the club!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.21,0:07:55.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底干嘛 下握还是随球把挥杆动作做完\N{\fs38}Well, which is it, choke up or follow-through?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.36,0:07:57.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jerry 拜托 我们说了好几次了\N{\fs38}Aww, come on, Jerry, we've been over this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.59,0:07:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个都要做到\N{\fs38}You know you got to do both!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.45,0:08:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们和你一样心烦\N{\fs38}This is as frustrating for us as it is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别来和我扯这些 这只会让我压力更大\N{\fs38}Don't tell me that! That just puts pressure on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.45,0:08:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 试着放松啦  - 你才该放松\N{\fs38}- Just try to relax. - You try to relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.38,0:08:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你试着放松过吗 真是自相矛盾\N{\fs38}Have you ever tried to relax?! It is a paradox!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.87,0:08:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些使命必达先生 可真棘手啊\N{\fs38}These Meeseeks, huh? Kind of a handful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.81,0:08:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们肯定也很头疼吧\N{\fs38}I can't imagine what you two must be going through.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:18.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jerry 我们的使命必达先生都已经消失几个小时了\N{\fs38}Our Meeseeks have been gone for hours, Jerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.68,0:08:19.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是在逗我吧\N{\fs38}You're kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.53,0:08:21.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意到什么变化没\N{\fs38}Notice anything different?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.34,0:08:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 你说几个小时前就消失了?\N{\fs38}I-I-I'm sorry. Hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.99,0:08:25.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸 看妈妈多美\N{\fs38}Dad, mom is a beautiful woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.07,0:08:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样会失去她的\N{\fs38}Look at her! You will lose her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:28.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃\N{\fs38}Uhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:31.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jerry 你能回来继续练习了嘛\N{\fs38}Hey, Jerry, you mind if we get back to the task at hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.37,0:08:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使命必达先生一般不需要存活这么久的\N{\fs38}Meeseeks don't usually have to exist this long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.06,0:08:35.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这感觉怪怪的\N{\fs38}It's getting weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:37.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法庭内保持肃静\N{\fs38}Order in the court!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.97,0:08:39.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在陪审团裁定前\N{\fs38}Before the jury reaches its verdict,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.90,0:08:44.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想先澄清 我个人认为你们两个是有罪的\N{\fs38}I just want to say that I consider you both very guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.27,0:08:45.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是奇妙的冒险啊 伙计\N{\fs38}Oh, great adventure, Buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.37,0:08:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rick和Morty进巨人监狱\N{\fs38}Rick and Morty go to giant prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.02,0:08:48.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是有人不小心掉块肥皂\N{\fs38}You know, if somebody drops the soap,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.66,0:08:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砸我们头上 我们的脊柱就直接被砸碎了 Morty\N{\fs38}it's gonna land on our heads and crush our spines, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.94,0:08:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后再奸尸多容易\N{\fs38}You know, i-i-i-it'll be really easy to rape us after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.74,0:08:54.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不会有事的 Rick\N{\fs38}We're gonna be okay, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.92,0:08:57.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想怎么做 他们把我的传送枪没收了\N{\fs38}How? They took my portal gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:08:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这案子一目了然 Morty\N{\fs38}This is an open-and-shut case, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.88,0:09:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得还能发生什么事吗\N{\fs38}You know, w-w-w-what do you think's gonna happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭空出现一个有魔力的天使 然后...\N{\fs38}some magical angel's gonna show up and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.17,0:09:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs38}Fee Fi Fo Fum\NFee! Fi! Fo! Fum!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.66,0:09:05.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我闻到了侵犯公民自由的味道\N{\fs38}I smell the violation of civil liberties!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法官大人 我来自一个迷你人倡导团体\N{\fs38}Your honor, I'm from a tiny-persons advocacy group
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.10,0:09:11.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来此是为了递交驳回此案的动议\N{\fs38}and I have here in my hand a motion to dismiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.11,0:09:14.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些迷你人未曾被告知他们的巨人权利\N{\fs38}These little men were never read their giant rights
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.02,0:09:16.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以应当被 fi释 fo放\N{\fs38}and are therefore free-fi to fo-home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.54,0:09:18.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他到底在说什么啊\N{\fs38}W-what the hell is he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.29,0:09:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的意思是他们自由了\N{\fs38}They're free to go, is what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.50,0:09:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我我我只是想贴近我们的口头禅而已\N{\fs38}I-I-I'm deconstructing our our thing we say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.31,0:09:25.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是巨人嘛 居然没人懂 算了随便吧\N{\fs38}We're giants. Nobody got that? Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.67,0:09:28.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就和你说嘛 Rick 我们做到了\N{\fs38}Oh, man, what did I tell you, Rick? We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.47,0:09:31.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 看来传送枪还能用\N{\fs38}All right, Morty, looks Like the portal gun's still working.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备回家了吗\N{\fs38}You ready to head home?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.61,0:09:34.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 这样你就逞心如意了不是嘛 Rick\N{\fs38}Oh, yeah, you'd like that, wouldn't you, Rick?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.42,0:09:36.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还不能放弃\N{\fs38}Well, you know what? We're not bailing out just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还要去找一些宝藏什么的\N{\fs38}You know, we're gonna go find some treasure or something
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.38,0:09:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带回去分给那些村民呢\N{\fs38}and we're gonna bring it to those villagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.49,0:09:44.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 别逞强了 这明显是徒劳无功\N{\fs38}Morty, cut your losses. This is obviously a wash.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.23,0:09:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我们一开始被捕的时候你也是这么说的\N{\fs38}Yeah, you were saying that back w-w-w-when we first got arrested,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.59,0:09:50.39,法院,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(284.572,128)\frx6\fry18\frz348.9}巨人法院
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.59,0:09:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(641.143,718.858)}现在我们被释放了 还大步流星的走出法院呢\N{\fs38}but here we are, you know, walking down the Courthouse steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.37,0:09:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪 Morty\N{\fs38}Oh, boy, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:57.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通常从法院的楼梯走下去是冒险里比较简单的部分\N{\fs38}Usually, walking down the Courthouse steps is the easy part of the adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.30,0:09:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说 Morty\N{\fs38}What do you say, Morty?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.39,0:10:01.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 帮把手 跟班\N{\fs38}I say give me a hand, Sidekick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:06.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是使命必达先生\N{\fs38}I'm Mr. Meeseeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都给我闭嘴 我再试试\N{\fs38}Everybody shut up! Let me try!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.89,0:10:13.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 可恶 可恶\N{\fs38}Damn it! Damn it! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.35,0:10:15.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我要出门了  - 哦 什么?\N{\fs38}- I'm going out. - Wait. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.32,0:10:17.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在忙 而我肚子饿了 所以想出去吃个饭\N{\fs38}Well, you're busy. I'm hungry. I thought I'd go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.81,0:10:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想让我开心呢 还是想让我被关起来\N{\fs38}Do you want me to be happy or do you want me to be in prison?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.27,0:10:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 哇 哇 你这脾气是... 我陪你去吃晚饭吧\N{\fs38}Whoa, whoa, where in the hell is... I'll take you to dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.00,0:10:25.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧\N{\fs38}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.07,0:10:27.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 听着 我也不愿意这么废柴\N{\fs38}Hey, you know what? It's hard being me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.32,0:10:28.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上就来\N{\fs38}I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.37,0:10:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 我的婚姻还亟待拯救呢\N{\fs38}Look, I've got a marriage to keep together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.83,0:10:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个挥杆的问题 更该操心的是你们 不是我\N{\fs38}At this point, my golf swing is more your problem than mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.97,0:10:39.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受不了了 我只想去死\N{\fs38}I can't take it anymore. I just want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.65,0:10:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都很想死啊 我们可是使命必达先生\N{\fs38}We all want to die! We're Meeseeks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.84,0:10:43.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要把我拖下水\N{\fs38}Why did you even rope me into this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.71,0:10:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他把我拖下水了啊\N{\fs38}'Cause he roped me into this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.36,0:10:47.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边那个 是他把我拖下水\N{\fs38}Well, him over there, he roped me into this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.68,0:10:49.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他把我拖下水\N{\fs38}Well, he roped me into this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:51.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我呢 是他把我拖下水\N{\fs38}Well, what about me? He roped me into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.35,0:10:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是被那边那个拖下水的\N{\fs38}Well, that one over there roped me into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.31,0:10:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他把我拖下水\N{\fs38}Well, he roped me into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.27,0:10:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 这种故事情节真是人人爱啊\N{\fs38}Yeah, Morty, this is the part of the story everybody loves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.74,0:11:02.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爬下650,000级巨型阶梯\N{\fs38}Scaling down 650,000 oversized steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵 如果这是一个故事\N{\fs38}All right, okay, y-you know, if this was a story,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.49,0:11:06.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这段就会被直接删掉了 白痴\N{\fs38}this part wouldn't be included, Stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.97,0:11:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rick 没想到吧 快看下面\N{\fs38}Hey, Rick, what do you know? Look down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.92,0:11:13.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像是个造在阶梯里的客栈\N{\fs38}Looks like some kind of tavern something built right into the side of the step.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.10,0:11:11.64,7,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\frx4\fry8\pos(836.571,370.286)\frz2.982}小渴栈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:17.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 Rick 这才像是一场冒险嘛\N{\fs38}Oh, wow, Rick. Now, this is more like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.55,0:11:20.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 这里有小小的阶梯形人\N{\fs38}Look, there's little staircase-shaped people in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.25,0:11:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各式各样稀奇古怪的角色呢\N{\fs38}A-all kinds of crazy characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.17,0:11:24.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这地方真棒\N{\fs38}This place is great, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.74,0:11:26.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稀奇古怪有很有趣\N{\fs38}It's whimsical and fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:29.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 妈的 你看什么看  - Rick 淡定\N{\fs38}- What are you looking at, mother f**ker. - Easy, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.89,0:11:33.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别理他们 这些阶梯小精灵脾气挺怪的\N{\fs38}Pay them no mind. Those stair goblins can be moody.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:35.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们想来点些什么\N{\fs38}Now, what can I getcha?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.69,0:11:38.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有斯伽洛罂粟\N{\fs38}We've got skarlog poppies,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.33,0:11:43.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放轰 哈鸡嗝丝 不撸基斯 多汁时间宝\N{\fs38}flurlow, halzingers, bloogies, juicy time babies...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.71,0:11:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随便啦 你们这里有苏格兰威士忌嘛\N{\fs38}Yeah yeah yeah. How about some scotch whiskey?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.98,0:11:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这你总有吧 还是只有一堆瞎扯的单词\N{\fs38}You got any of that around here? Or just a bunch of nonsense words?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.68,0:11:50.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rick 请给我们两杯不撸基斯\N{\fs38}Rick. We'll have two bloogies, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.61,0:11:52.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 我们想问\N{\fs38}And, uh, we were wondering,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.29,0:11:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有让两名英雄更快下楼梯的办法么\N{\fs38}is there a faster way two heroes could get down these stairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.42,0:11:57.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们需要搭便车吗\N{\fs38}Y'all need to ride down the stairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.66,0:12:00.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字是滑溜顺滑小阶梯\N{\fs38}My name is Slippely-Slippery Stair.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:04.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,25傻 我就能背你们下去\N{\fs38}I'll take you down there for 25 shmeckels.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.85,0:12:08.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,25傻 那是什么东西啊\N{\fs38}25 shmeckels? I don't know how much I don't know what that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.04,0:12:09.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是很多 还是很少\N{\fs38}Is that a lot? Is it a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.38,0:12:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这对硕大的假胸也是这价钱\N{\fs38}That's exactly how much I spent on my big fake boobies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.09,0:12:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨 我是买胸达人先生 我愿意出25傻怕蛘舛孕夭\N{\fs38}Hi, I'm Mr. Booby Buyer. I'll buy those boobies for 25 shmeckels.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.56,0:12:18.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好诱人的开价 但我还是拒绝好了\N{\fs38}It's a tempting offer, but I'm gonna have to decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.52,0:12:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 太可惜了\N{\fs38}Rats! What a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.37,0:12:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 你的冒险没什么前途了\N{\fs38}Morty, your adventure's in a spiral.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.28,0:12:24.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说真的 是时候该走了\N{\fs38}For real, man, time to pull out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rick 你知道你为什么老质疑我的冒险吗\N{\fs38}You keep heckling my adventure, Rick! You know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.45,0:12:27.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 因为很烂\N{\fs38}Uh, because it's lame?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:28.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你小肚鸡肠\N{\fs38}It's because you're petty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.47,0:12:33.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为了你忍受了多少扯淡的破事儿\N{\fs38}You know, h-how many times have I had to follow you into some nonsensical bull crap?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.11,0:12:35.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我每次都忍了 Rick\N{\fs38}I always roll with the punches, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你就不行\N{\fs38}Why can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.03,0:12:38.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 我要去上个厕所 等我回来的时候\N{\fs38}Look, I got to take a leak, and when I come back,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.30,0:12:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你还是没有想通的话 你就自己回去吧\N{\fs38}if you haven't learned how to lighten up, don't be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.97,0:12:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随你便\N{\fs38}Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.67,0:12:45.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事态已经很明显了 看过来\N{\fs38}It's become clear, look at me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.34,0:12:48.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我们专攻Jerry的后续打姿\N{\fs38}that if we concentrate all our efforts on Jerry's follow-through,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:51.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题就能解决了 我是使命必达先生\N{\fs38}we will solve this problem. I'm Mr. Meeseeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:53.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是使命必达先生 看过来\N{\fs38}I'm Mr. Meeseeks. Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.70,0:12:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正解应该是要让他正确握杆\N{\fs38}The only thing that's clear is that choking up is the one true solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.61,0:12:59.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看过来 我是使命必达先生\N{\fs38}Look at me. I'm Mr. Meeseeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.23,0:13:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经在这里帮Jerry两天了\N{\fs38}I've been trying to help Jerry for two days,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:04.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对使命必达先生来说已经算是永恒了\N{\fs38}an eternity in Meeseeks time,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.07,0:13:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是什么都没能奏效\N{\fs38}and nothing's worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:06.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最担心的是我\N{\fs38}I fear the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.47,0:13:08.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的失败属于你一个人 老头\N{\fs38}Your failures are your own, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是使命必达先生 看过来 我说后续打姿\N{\fs38}I'm Mr. Meeseeks! Look at me. I say follow-through!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.58,0:13:14.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 谁支持我?  - 后续打姿\N{\fs38}- Who's with me?! - Follow-through.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.40,0:13:17.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是使命必达先生 看过来\N{\fs38}I'm Mr. Meeseeks! Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.41,0:13:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 杀了他  - 妈的\N{\fs38}- Kill him! - Son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.37,0:13:27.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 我是软豆先生\N{\fs38}How are you today? I'm Mr. Jelly Bean.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.31,0:13:29.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨 软豆先生 我是Morty\N{\fs38}Hi, Mr. Jelly Bean. I'm Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.43,0:13:31.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我外公和我是来冒险的\N{\fs38}My grandpa and I are on an adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.07,0:13:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒 有趣吗\N{\fs38}Nice. Is it a fun adventure?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.46,0:13:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望吧\N{\fs38}I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我开始担心是不是有点脱离正轨了\N{\fs38}But I'm starting to get nervous that maybe it's gone a little too far off the rails.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冒险不都这样的嘛\N{\fs38}Isn't that what adventures do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.80,0:13:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 你说的很对\N{\fs38}Hey, you know what? You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.07,0:13:43.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都挺顺利的\N{\fs38}Everything's going fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.56,0:13:46.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要放轻松 顺其自然就好\N{\fs38}I just got to relax and go with the flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.25,0:13:47.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs38}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.82,0:13:52.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 啊 那个 拜拜 - 不 别走啊\N{\fs38}- Okay. Uh. Bye. - Uhh, no, stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.46,0:13:53.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟着感觉走\N{\fs38}Go with the flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.71,0:13:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 你让我现在很不舒服\N{\fs38}Stop. You're making me really uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.37,0:13:59.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要抗拒我 顺其自然就好\N{\fs38}Stop fighting me. Just let this happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.59,0:14:00.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚开啊\N{\fs38}Get off of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.87,0:14:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*美丽家园阿拉巴马*\N{\fs38}*Sweet home Alabama*
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.37,0:14:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊 住手 求求你\N{\fs38}No! Stop! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.08,0:14:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么[哔]的风骚啊 你个小[哔]\N{\fs38}Stop being such a ** tease, you sweet little **.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.37,0:14:24.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 住手\N{\fs38}No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.37,0:14:40.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都给我停下\N{\fs38}Everybody sto-o-o-p!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.47,0:14:41.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看过来\N{\fs38}Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.50,0:14:46.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的兄弟们啊 在这里流血起不到任何作用\N{\fs38}My brothers, nothing will be accomplished by shedding Meeseeks blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.16,0:14:49.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请求不被满足我们是不会死去的\N{\fs38}None of us can die until our job is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.04,0:14:50.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个请求根本无法满足\N{\fs38}The job can't be done!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.56,0:14:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不可能帮他减去两杆\N{\fs38}We'll never get two strokes off his game!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.50,0:14:53.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不能\N{\fs38}No, we won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.63,0:14:57.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们可以帮他减掉所有的杆数\N{\fs38}But we will get all strokes off his game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.01,0:14:59.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 他想到哪里去了  - 他什么意思\N{\fs38}- Where's he going with this? - What's he mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.28,0:15:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在他生命终止的那一刻\N{\fs38}When we kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:07.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jerry 或许是时候 我去参加那个我一直向往的旅行了\N{\fs38}Jerry, maybe it's time I take that trip I always talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.37,0:15:08.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪里\N{\fs38}Where would you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.56,0:15:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是道 意大利 希腊 阿根廷\N{\fs38}I don't know, man. Italy. Greece. Argentina.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.99,0:15:15.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些国家的男人性欲都很旺盛呢\N{\fs38}Countries known for their sexually aggressive men.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.97,0:15:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你说过 其实我很喜欢你的新发型吗\N{\fs38}Did I tell you how much I love your new haircut?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.87,0:15:21.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我靠 发生什么事了\N{\fs38}What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.87,0:15:24.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在那里\N{\fs38}There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.37,0:15:28.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃 Jerry\N{\fs38}Run, Jerry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.37,0:15:33.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快出来吧 Jerry\N{\fs38}Come on out, Jerry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.67,0:15:37.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会好好握杆的 我会做好后续打姿的 你们说什么我就做什么\N{\fs38}Guys, I'll choke up. I'll follow through. I'll do whatever you tell me to do, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经用不着了 Jerry\N{\fs38}Oh, we're well past that, Jerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.97,0:15:46.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点 Rick 别拖时间了 你手里啥牌\N{\fs38}Come on, Rick, quit stalling. What do ya got?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.05,0:15:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看完了就去角落哭吧\N{\fs38}Read 'em and weep, fellas!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.45,0:15:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 Morty\N{\fs38}Oh, hey, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:53.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 之前说了很多关冒险的坏话 我很抱歉\N{\fs38}Listen, I'm really sorry about all that stuff I said earlier about your adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.23,0:15:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在很开心 Morty\N{\fs38}I'm havin' a good time, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.10,0:15:55.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实没有这么糟\N{\fs38}It's not so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.73,0:15:56.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们回家吧\N{\fs38}Let's just go home, Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.83,0:15:57.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我放弃了\N{\fs38}I'm calling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.73,0:15:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冒险到此为止\N{\fs38}The adventure's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.67,0:15:59.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在还不能走啊 Morty\N{\fs38}We can't leave now, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.81,0:16:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这手气 拦不住啊\N{\fs38}I'm on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.03,0:16:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在就想走\N{\fs38}Look, I want to leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赌约是你赢了 好嘛\N{\fs38}You win the bet, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.17,0:16:05.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把传送枪给我 我们走吧\N{\fs38}Just give me the portal gun and let's go, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.37,0:16:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你了 我只想回家\N{\fs38}Please, I just want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.97,0:16:13.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着Morty 我刚刚赢了一堆傻\N{\fs38}Listen, Morty. I just won a bunch of shmeckels.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.32,0:16:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们用25傻湃盟郴小阶梯载我们回去\N{\fs38}Why don't we use 25 of them to pay Slippery Stair here for a ride back to the village,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.05,0:16:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后把剩余的傻鸥村民怎么样\N{\fs38}and then we'll give the rest of the shmeckels to the villagers, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.94,0:16:21.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嘛\N{\fs38}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:22.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 Morty\N{\fs38}Sure, Morty. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.42,0:16:24.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的冒险需要一个好的结局\N{\fs38}You know, a good adventure needs a good ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.34,0:16:27.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐稳咯\N{\fs38}Buckle up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:36.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使命必达先生来到这个世界上不是为了寻求意义的 Jerry\N{\fs38}Meeseeks are not born into this world fumbling for meaning, Jerry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.47,0:16:39.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的存在只为了满足一个愿望\N{\fs38}We are created to serve a singular purpose
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.51,0:16:42.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了实现这个愿望我们可以不择手段\N{\fs38}for which we will go to any lengths to fulfill!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.75,0:16:45.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在于世上对我们来说是痛苦的 Jerry\N{\fs38}Existence is pain to a Meeseeks, Jerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.61,0:16:49.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们为了减去痛苦可以不择手段 就问...\N{\fs38}And we will do anything to alleviate that pain. Just ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.07,0:16:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫什么 女士\N{\fs38}What's your name, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.20,0:16:55.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Samantha 求求你 先生 他要什么就给他吧\N{\fs38}S-samantha. Please, Mister! Give him what he wants!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.37,0:16:58.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无辜的人要因我而死了\N{\fs38}Innocent people are going to die because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.44,0:17:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为什么就这么平庸呢\N{\fs38}Why am I so mediocre?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.77,0:17:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jerry 转身 挺背\N{\fs38}Jerry, turn around. Straighten your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.76,0:17:07.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弯膝 弯下去\N{\fs38}Bend your knees. Bend them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.69,0:17:11.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肩膀往后 深吸一口气\N{\fs38}Square your shoulders. Take a deep breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.77,0:17:13.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\fs38}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.57,0:17:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我数到三 Jerry\N{\fs38}I'm counting to three, Jerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.45,0:17:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这[哔]的是在搞什么\N{\fs38}What the f**k is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.83,0:17:35.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他成功了\N{\fs38}He's got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.91,0:17:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一下能减不少差点了\N{\fs38}Th-th-that's a lower handicap stro-o-ke!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.57,0:17:45.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 但是我是个比较顽固的使命必达先生\N{\fs38}Excuse me. I'm a bit of a stickler Meeseeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.39,0:17:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的近距离击球呢\N{\fs38}What about your short game?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.89,0:17:49.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪 天哪 我的天哪\N{\fs38}Oh, my god, oh, my god!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:51.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的近距离击球呢\N{\fs38}What about your short game?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.87,0:17:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 好棒\N{\fs38}Ooh, nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.97,0:18:06.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我们还是打包就好\N{\fs38}I think we'll take our food to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.61,0:18:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想都别想\N{\fs38}No, you won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.39,0:18:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警察要来了 你有很多问题得慢慢回答呢\N{\fs38}The police are coming. You have so many questions to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.43,0:18:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs38}Fair enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.37,0:18:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 好心的先生 我们的村子有救了\N{\fs38}Thank you, kind sir. Our village is saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.37,0:18:22.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们可真是真英雄啊\N{\fs38}You are both true heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.57,0:18:28.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好样的 Morty 看来赌约是你赢了\N{\fs38}Good job, Morty. Looks like you won the bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.57,0:18:30.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢啦 Rick 但我也不知道其实该不该赢呢\N{\fs38}Thanks, Rick, but I don't know if I should.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.86,0:18:32.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实关于宇宙的看法你是对的\N{\fs38}You know, you were right about the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.42,0:18:34.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是疯狂而混乱啊\N{\fs38}It's a crazy and chaotic place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.40,0:18:38.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以每过一段时间就得清扫一下嘛\N{\fs38}Well, you know, maybe that's why it could use a little cleaning up every now and then, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.25,0:18:41.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的冒险这么棒 是因为我们是按Morty的方式来的呀\N{\fs38}This one's wrapped up neat and clean because we did it Morty style.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.65,0:18:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英雄们 我希望把你们介绍给我们的国王\N{\fs38}Oh! Heroes, we would like to introduce you to our beloved King
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.53,0:18:47.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好让他亲自感谢你们\N{\fs38}so that he may thank you personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.47,0:18:49.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 其实不用了啦\N{\fs38}Uh, no, i-it's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.97,0:18:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rick 传送门 快\N{\fs38}Rick. Portal. Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.92,0:19:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 你还在考虑去旅行吗\N{\fs38}So... You still thinking about taking that trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.77,0:19:10.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jerry 听着\N{\fs38}Jerry, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.02,0:19:13.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我们的婚姻不完美 但是我哪里也不会去的\N{\fs38}We don't have a perfect marriage, but I'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.27,0:19:14.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在那冷藏室里的时候\N{\fs38}When we were in that freezer,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.77,0:19:18.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我意识到那些使命必达先生就和我高中时候的男生一样\N{\fs38}I realized the Meeseeks are like the guys I went to high school with.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.38,0:19:20.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了完成自己的"使命"说什么都愿意\N{\fs38}Willing to say anything to "complete their task."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.94,0:19:22.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是其中一员嘛\N{\fs38}Was I one of those guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.86,0:19:26.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,区别就在于你没有消失\N{\fs38}The difference is you didn't disappear afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.01,0:19:28.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为 我害你怀孕了嘛\N{\fs38}Well... I got you pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.05,0:19:30.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs38}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.37,0:19:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事\N{\fs38}What the hell happened to this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.14,0:19:33.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的使命必达盒子\N{\fs38}Uh, your Meeseeks box happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.89,0:19:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们因为减不掉Jerry的两杆崩溃了\N{\fs38}They went crazy when they couldn't take two strokes off Jerry's golf game.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.42,0:19:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可内疚了\N{\fs38}He felt terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.34,0:19:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jerry智商低又不是我的问题\N{\fs38}Hey, it's not my fault that Jerry's an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.93,0:19:43.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸 你有什么能帮忙清理这里的东西嘛\N{\fs38}Dad! Is there anything you can do to clean this place up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.72,0:19:45.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有一个清理必备盒子\N{\fs38}Well, you know, I do have a Fleeseeks box.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.70,0:19:47.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 不能再用盒子了\N{\fs38}No. No more boxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:49.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 盒子里就一个拖把和地板蜡\N{\fs38}What? It just has a mop and some floor wax in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.95,0:19:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs38}Wubba lubba dub dubs\NWubba lubba dub dubs!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.97,0:19:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的新台词\N{\fs38}Yeah! That's my new thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.54,0:19:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像那个 叫Arsenio的家伙\N{\fs38}I'm kind of like what's his name Ar-arsenio.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.54,0:20:01.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}Arsenio Hall 美国喜剧演员
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.20,0:19:58.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是Arsenio在台节目里经常说的\N{\fs38}Isn't that it's what Arsenio used to say on his show.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.63,0:20:01.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wobble gobba lop bops对吧\N{\fs38}Wobble gobba lop bops! Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.07,0:20:02.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 我们下周再见\N{\fs38}See you next week, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.11,0:20:03.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑点完全没有懂\N{\fs38}I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.14,0:20:37.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生 你得看看这个\N{\fs38}Sir, I think you're going to want to see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.08,0:20:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在软豆国王衣橱里的保险柜找到了这个\N{\fs38}We found it inside a lockbox inside King Jelly Bean's closet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.23,0:20:44.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们应该把这事公布于众\N{\fs38}We have to tell the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:47.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 还是毁掉吧\N{\fs38}Wait. Destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.55,0:20:57.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对人民而言 更有意义的是他所代表的价值和理念\N{\fs38}Our people will get more from the idea he represented
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.20,0:21:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而不是他的真实面貌\N{\fs38}than from the Jelly Bean he actually was.

